_aChangeLog.text: Fixed glitch where you would get stopped by Osu stages.

_sText:
Around 30 minutes for the average bhopper. 

If the map is renamed you will lose all the soundscapes, i did this with sina_fix. if you want the sound back you can just remove the _fix. Sorry about that. 

Thanks Sirhephaestus and Dream for testing. 

Thanks Pcpie for figuring out how to fix getting stopped by the Osu stage blocks!
